model.houm.goals_current.raw_sql:
WITH GoalsCurrent AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('rentals_units') }}
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('sales_units') }}
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('sales_local_revenue')}}
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('eop_subs')}}
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('cum_sales_units')}}
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('cum_rentals_units')}}
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM {{ref('cum_sales_local_revenue')}})

SELECT 
/* NO PIVOT IN REDSHIFT */
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'units' THEN total END) as units,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'acc_units' THEN total END) as acc_units,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'local_revenue' THEN total END) AS local_revenue,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'acc_local_revenue' THEN total END) AS acc_local_revenue,
metric,country,date_month
FROM GoalsCurrent
GROUP BY country,metric,date_month
model.houm.goals_current.name: goals_current
model.houm.goals_current.compiled_sql:
WITH GoalsCurrent AS (
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."processing_finance"."rentals_units"
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."processing_finance"."sales_units"
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."processing_finance"."sales_local_revenue"
UNION ALL
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."processing_finance"."eop_subs"
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."public"."cum_sales_units"
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."public"."cum_rentals_units"
UNION ALL 
SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."public"."cum_sales_local_revenue")

SELECT 
/* NO PIVOT IN REDSHIFT */
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'units' THEN total END) as units,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'acc_units' THEN total END) as acc_units,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'local_revenue' THEN total END) AS local_revenue,
SUM(CASE WHEN col = 'acc_local_revenue' THEN total END) AS acc_local_revenue,
metric,country,date_month
FROM GoalsCurrent
GROUP BY country,metric,date_month

model.houm.cum_rentals_units.raw_sql:
SELECT
    'rentals_transactions' as metric,
    'acc_units' as col,
    country,
    date_month,
    SUM(total) over (
        PARTITION BY country
        ORDER BY
            date_month rows unbounded preceding
    ) AS cum_total
FROM
    {{ ref('rentals_units') }}
WHERE date_month >= concat(extract(year from current_date),'-01-01')
ORDER BY
    country,
    date_month

model.houm.sales_seller_metric_leads.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH metric AS (
SELECT 
	* 
FROM {{ ref('sales_seller_metric_details_leads') }}
)

SELECT
	orden , 
	metric ,	
	geo_id ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN yesterday = 1 THEN email END ) AS yesterday ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN daybeforeyesterday = 1 THEN email END ) AS daybeforeyesterday ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastWeek = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastWeek ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PastLastWeek = 1 THEN email END ) AS PastLastWeek ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ThisMonthtoday = 1 THEN email END ) AS ThisMonthtoday ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastMonthtoday = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastMonthtoday , 
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastMonth = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastMonth ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LasttwoMonth = 1 THEN email END ) AS LasttwoMonth ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastthreeMonth = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastthreeMonth 
FROM metric 
GROUP BY 1,2,3

model.houm.properties_published.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

SELECT 
        a.id as property_id
        ,b.status as rental_status
        ,c.status as sales_status
        ,a.*
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }} a
left join {{ ref('proc_propertydetails') }} b on a.id = b.property_id 
left join {{ ref('proc_property_salesdetails') }} c on a.id = c.property_id
where b.status in ('published','republished') or c.status in ('published','republished')
model.houm.properties_published.name: properties_published

model.houm.sales_investor_metric_leads_q.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH metric AS (
SELECT 
	* 
FROM {{ ref('sales_investor_metric_details_leads_qualified_date') }}
)

SELECT 
	orden , 
	metric ,	
	geo_id ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN yesterday = 1 THEN email END ) AS yesterday ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN daybeforeyesterday = 1 THEN email END ) AS daybeforeyesterday ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastWeek = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastWeek ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PastLastWeek = 1 THEN email END ) AS PastLastWeek ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ThisMonthtoday = 1 THEN email END ) AS ThisMonthtoday ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastMonthtoday = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastMonthtoday , 
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastMonth = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastMonth ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LasttwoMonth = 1 THEN email END ) AS LasttwoMonth ,
	COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LastthreeMonth = 1 THEN email END ) AS LastthreeMonth 
FROM metric 
GROUP BY 1,2,3

model.houm.dim_dates.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='view') }}


 SELECT
    cast(seq + 1 AS INTEGER)                                      AS date_id,
-- DATE
    datum                                                         AS full_date,
    TO_CHAR(datum, 'DD/MM/YYYY') :: CHAR(10)                      AS au_format_date,
    TO_CHAR(datum, 'MM/DD/YYYY') :: CHAR(10)                      AS us_format_date,
-- YEAR
    cast(extract(YEAR FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                    AS year_number,
    cast(extract(WEEK FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                    AS year_week_number,
    cast(extract(DOY FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                     AS year_day_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '6' MONTH, 'yyyy') AS SMALLINT) AS au_fiscal_year_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '3' MONTH, 'yyyy') AS SMALLINT) AS us_fiscal_year_number,
-- QUARTER
    cast(to_char(datum, 'Q') AS SMALLINT)                         AS qtr_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '6' MONTH, 'Q') AS SMALLINT)    AS au_fiscal_qtr_number,
    cast(to_char(datum + INTERVAL '3' MONTH, 'Q') AS SMALLINT)    AS us_fiscal_qtr_number,
-- MONTH
    cast(extract(MONTH FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                   AS month_number,
    to_char(datum, 'Month')                                       AS month_name,
    cast(extract(DAY FROM datum) AS SMALLINT)                     AS month_day_number,
-- WEEK
    cast(to_char(datum, 'D') AS SMALLINT)                         AS week_day_number,
-- DAY
    to_char(datum, 'Day')                                         AS day_name,
    CASE WHEN to_char(datum, 'D') IN ('1', '7')
      THEN 0
    ELSE 1 END                                                    AS day_is_weekday,
    CASE WHEN
      extract(DAY FROM (datum + (1 - extract(DAY FROM datum)) :: INTEGER +
                        INTERVAL '1' MONTH) :: DATE -
                       INTERVAL '1' DAY) = extract(DAY FROM datum)
      THEN 1
    ELSE 0 END                                                    AS day_is_last_of_month
  FROM
    (
      SELECT
        '2018-01-01' :: DATE + generate_series AS datum,
        generate_series                        AS seq
      FROM generate_series(0, 7 * 365, 1)
    ) DQ
  ORDER BY 1 desc

model.houm.rental_landlord_metric_detail.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH paid_media_cost AS (
SELECT *
FROM  {{ ref('proc_marketing_paid_media') }} AS proc_marketing_paid_media 
WHERE TRUE
    AND geo_id IS NOT NULL
    AND business_marketing = 'Landlord'
    AND funnel_marketing = 'Supply'
)

SELECT    
    10::INT AS orden ,
    'Paid Media Cost (USD)'::TEXT AS metric ,
    geo_id , 
    '{{ var("processed_time") }}' AS processed_time ,
    executed_at ,
    day_cost ,
    day_clicks , 
    day_impressions ,
    CASE WHEN executed_at = DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS yesterday ,
    CASE WHEN executed_at = DATEADD(DAY,-2,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS daybeforeyesterday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',executed_at) = DATEADD(WEEK,-1, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',executed_at) = DATEADD(WEEK,-2, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS PastLastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::date) 
           AND executed_at <= DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ThisMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN 
          DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) )  AND  
          executed_at <= DATEADD(MONTH,-1, '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-3, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth 
FROM paid_media_cost
ORDER BY executed_at DESC

    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_sales)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           AND (TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_sales)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE <= DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ThisMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_sales)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) AND 
           (TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_sales)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE  <= DATEADD(MONTH,-1, '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonthtoday , 
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_sales)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_sales)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth ,

           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth

LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz

ORDER BY date_sales DESC

{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH rental_properties AS (
SELECT
    id AS property_id ,
    country ,
    for_rental ,
    first_publication_date AS date_rentals
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }} 
WHERE TRUE 
        AND first_publication_date IS NOT NULL 
        AND is_deleted = FALSE 
)

SELECT     
    80::INT AS orden ,
    'New Rental Listing'::TEXT AS metric , 
    geo_id , 
    '{{ var("processed_time") }}' AS processed_time ,
    COALESCE((TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE,date_rentals::DATE) AS date_rentals ,
    rental_properties.property_id ,
    CASE WHEN (TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE  = DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS yesterday ,
    CASE WHEN (TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE  = DATEADD(DAY,-2,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS daybeforeyesterday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(WEEK,-1, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(WEEK,-2, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS PastLastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           AND (TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE <= DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ThisMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) AND 
           (TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE <= DATEADD(MONTH,-1, '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonthtoday , 
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth , 
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',(TIMEZONE( prop_mz.timezone, date_rentals)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE ) = DATEADD(MONTH,-3, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth
FROM rental_properties
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} prop_mz 
        ON rental_properties.property_id = prop_mz.property_id 
ORDER BY date_rentals DESC

WITH schedules_photo_clean AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('proc_supply_schedules') }}
WHERE TRUE 
   AND schedule_type_name = 'Photo' 
   AND (
      ( email NOT LIKE '%test.test' 
      AND email NOT LIKE '%test.com')  
      OR applicant_id IS NULL )
)

    50::INT AS orden , 
    'Photo Created'::TEXT AS metric ,
    geo_id ,
    '{{ var("processed_time") }}' AS processed_time ,
    created_at ,
    schedule_id ,
    CASE WHEN created_at = DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS yesterday ,
    CASE WHEN created_at = DATEADD(DAY,-2,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS daybeforeyesterday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',created_at) = DATEADD(WEEK,-1, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',created_at) = DATEADD(WEEK,-2, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS PastLastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',created_at) =  DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           AND created_at <= DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ThisMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',created_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) AND 
           created_at <= DATEADD(MONTH,-1, '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonthtoday , 
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',created_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',created_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth , 
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',created_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-3, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth
FROM schedules_photo_clean
ORDER BY created_at DESC

model.houm.fact_daily_virtual_uf_cl.raw_sql:
with table6 as (
select row_number() over (order by thedate asc) as n_day
 	,thefirstofmonth 
 	,thedate
 	,b.monthly_inflation
 	,b.daily_inflation
 	,lead(daily_inflation,1) over (order by thedate asc) as next_daily_inflation
from dim_dates a
left join {{ ref('proc_monthly_daily_inflation_cl') }} b on a.thefirstofmonth  = b.date_formatted 
order by thedate asc
)
, table7 as (
select thedate
		,n_day
		,monthly_inflation
		,daily_inflation
		--,(SUM(1 * (1+daily_inflation) ) OVER(ORDER BY thedate ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)-(n_day-1)) as try_1
from table6
where monthly_inflation is not null
order by n_day
)

select 
	n_day
	,thedate
	,monthly_inflation
	,daily_inflation
	,exp(sum(ln(1+daily_inflation)) over (ORDER BY thedate ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)) as  daily_virtual_uf
from table7

WITH paid_media_cost AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('proc_marketing_paid_media') }} AS proc_marketing_paid_media 
WHERE TRUE
    AND geo_id IS NOT NULL
    AND business_marketing = 'Buyer New Properties'
    AND funnel_marketing = 'Demand'
)

SELECT    
    20::INT AS orden ,
    'Paid Media Cost NP (USD)'::TEXT AS metric ,
    geo_id , 
    '{{ var("processed_time") }}' AS processed_time ,
    executed_at ,
    day_cost ,
    day_clicks , 
    day_impressions ,
    CASE WHEN executed_at = DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS yesterday ,
    CASE WHEN executed_at = DATEADD(DAY,-2,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE)  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS daybeforeyesterday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',executed_at) = DATEADD(WEEK,-1, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',executed_at) = DATEADD(WEEK,-2, DATE_TRUNC('week','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS PastLastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) =  DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::date) 
           AND executed_at <= DATEADD(DAY,-1,'{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ThisMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN 
          DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) =  DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) )  AND  
          executed_at <= DATEADD(MONTH,-1, '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',executed_at) = DATEADD(MONTH,-3, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
          THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth 
FROM paid_media_cost
ORDER BY executed_at DESC

    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',buyer_qualification_date) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth , 
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',buyer_qualification_date) = DATEADD(MONTH,-3, DATE_TRUNC('month','{{ var("processed_time") }}'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth
FROM demand_sales_leads_clean
WHERE TRUE 
        AND buyer_qualification >= 3  
        AND buyer_qualification <= 5
        AND buyer_qualification_date IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY buyer_qualification_date DESC

SELECT *
FROM "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_demand_sales_leads"
WHERE TRUE 
AND ( 
        (lost_reason NOT LIKE '%Test%'  
        AND lost_reason != 'Pruebas'  
        AND lost_reason != 'Cotización Duplicada') 
        OR lost_reason IS  NULL )
AND (buyer_relation_negotiation = 'Usados')
)

    '2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00' AS processed_time ,
    add_time ,
    buyer_qualification ,
    buyer_qualification_date ,
    person_id ,
    email ,

    CASE WHEN buyer_qualification_date = DATEADD(DAY,-2,'2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS daybeforeyesterday ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',buyer_qualification_date) = DATEADD(WEEK,-1, DATE_TRUNC('week','2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('week',buyer_qualification_date) = DATEADD(WEEK,-2, DATE_TRUNC('week','2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS PastLastWeek ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',buyer_qualification_date) = DATE_TRUNC('month','2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) 
           AND buyer_qualification_date <= DATEADD(DAY,-1,'2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ThisMonthtoday ,
    CASE WHEN 
           DATE_TRUNC('month',buyer_qualification_date) = DATEADD(MONTH,-1, DATE_TRUNC('month','2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) ) AND 
           buyer_qualification_date <= DATEADD(MONTH,-1, '2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE)

           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastMonth ,
    CASE WHEN DATE_TRUNC('month',buyer_qualification_date) = DATEADD(MONTH,-2, DATE_TRUNC('month','2022-06-20 13:13:24.436303-04:00'::DATE) ) 
           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LasttwoMonth ,

           THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LastthreeMonth
FROM demand_sales_leads_clean

        AND buyer_qualification >= 3  
        AND buyer_qualification <= 5

model.houm.stg_zendesk_metrics.name: stg_zendesk_metrics
model.houm.stg_zendesk_metrics.description:
Table with commons metrics about the tickets, more info consult:

https://developer.zendesk.com/api-reference/ticketing/tickets/ticket_metrics/

The important columns are:
- assigned_at: *When the ticket was assigned*
- created_at: *When the ticket was created*
- first_resolution_time_in_minutes
- full_resolution_time_in_minutes
- latest_comment_added_at
- initially_assigned_at: *When the ticket was initially assigned*
- agent_wait_time_in_minutes: *Number of minutes the agent spent waiting during calendar and business hours* 
- solved_at: *When the ticket was solved*
- ticket_id: unique id of the tickets. ** Can be related with the table tickets_audits or tickets.**

model.houm.stg_zendesk_tickets_audits.name: stg_zendesk_tickets_audits
model.houm.stg_zendesk_tickets_audits.description:
Audits are a read-only history of all updates to a ticket. 
 				When a ticket is updated in Zendesk Support, an audit is stored. 
 				Each audit represents a single update to the ticket.
  				An update can consist of one or more events, ex: 	
  											- The value of a ticket field was changed
											- A new comment was added
											- Tags were added or	 removed
											- A notification was sent
The more important columns are:
 - via = * Describes how the object was created. See the [Via object  reference](https://developer.zendesk.com/documentation/ticketing/reference-guides/ticket-audit-events-reference) * 
 - events = * An array of the events that happened in this audit. See the [Ticket Audit events reference](https://developer.zendesk.com/documentation/ticketing/reference-guides/via-object-reference/)* 
 - metadata = * Metadata for the audit, custom and system data, info acerca del navegador y SO que se ocupó * 
 - author_id = * The user who created the audit * 
 - ticket_id = * The ID of the associated ticket *
 - created_at = * The time the audit was created *

model.houm.stg_zendesk_tickets.name: stg_zendesk_tickets
model.houm.stg_zendesk_tickets.description:
Tickets are the means through which your end users (customers) communicate with agents in Zendesk Support. Tickets can originate from a number of channels, including email, Help Center, chat, phone call, Twitter, Facebook, or the API. 

All tickets have a core set of properties.
 source: https://developer.zendesk.com/api-reference/ticketing/tickets/tickets/


The more important columns are:
- id: *unique ticket id at zendesk Houm*
- created_at: * ticket creation timestamp *
- updated_at: * ticket update timestamp *
- status: * All tickets in Zendesk Support start out as New and progress through Open, Pending, Solved, and Closed states. A ticket must have an assignee in order to be solved. * 
- tags: array of tags 
- priority: this is a priority of the ticket, can be: [urgent, normal, high, low, null]
- **submitter_id**: This is the agent id, The user who submitted the ticket. The submitter always becomes the author of the first comment on the ticket
- **requester_id**: This is the customer id, The user who requested this ticket.
- **assignee_id**: This is the agent id, that currently asigned to solve this ticket.

id.description: This is a unique identifier for the tickets

created_at.name: created_at
created_at.description: This is a timestamp for the created time of the ticket

updated_at.name: updated_at
updated_at.description: This is a timestamp for the last update of the ticket

status.name: status
status.description: This is a represent of the state of the tickets, can be [solved,open,closed,deleted,pending,new]. All tickets in Zendesk Support start out as New and progress through Open, Pending, Solved, and Closed states. A ticket must have an assignee in order to be solved.

prority.name: prority
prority.description: This is the priority ticket, can be urgent,normal,high,low. This come from the initial form

type.name: type
type.description: This is type of the ticket is, can be null, problem, task, incident, question. This come from the initial form

tags.name: tags
tags.description: This is an array of the tags of the tickets. This come from the initial form

subject.name: subject
subject.description: This is description of the initial comment of the ticket

requester_id.name: requester_id
requester_id.description: This is the customer id, The user who requested this ticket.

submitter_id.name: submitter_id
submitter_id.description: This is the agent id, The user who submitted the ticket. The submitter always becomes the author of the first comment on the ticket

model.houm.stg_monthly_inflation_mx.raw_sql:
with table1 as ( --renaming columns and drop duplicates
SELECT idserie
		,titulo
		,to_date(date, 'YYYY-DD-MM', FALSE) as date_formatted 
		,value
FROM {{ source('raw_stage', 'series_ipc_mx') }}
group by idserie,titulo,date,value
)
, table2 as ( --get next period value
SELECT *
		,lead(date_formatted,1) OVER(order by date_formatted ASC) as next_date
		,lead(value,1) OVER(order by date_formatted ASC) as next_value
FROM table1
order by date_formatted
), table3 as ( -- get number of days per month
SELECT 
	min(thedate) as  full_date
	,theyear
	,themonth
	,count(*) as n_days
FROM dim_dates 
group by theyear,themonth 
order by theyear,themonth 
)
, table4 as ( --calculate the monthly inflation
SELECT a.date_formatted
		,((next_value-value)/next_value) as  monthly_inflation
	    ,b.n_days
FROM table2 a
left join table3 b on a.date_formatted = b.full_date::date
)

SELECT * 
FROM table4

model.houm.proc_closure_subs.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH plans_clean AS (
SELECT 
   plans.id ,
   plans.name ,
   plans.description , 
   plans.has_management
FROM {{ ref('proc_closure_plans') }} AS plans
WHERE TRUE 
   AND ( 
        (plans.name NOT LIKE '%(test)%'
        AND plans.name NOT LIKE 'AAA' )
        OR plans.name IS NULL )
   AND ( 
        ( plans.description NOT LIKE '% prueba'
        AND plans.description NOT LIKE '% test') 
        OR plans.description IS NULL
        ) 
)

, contracts_clean AS (
SELECT 
   contracts.id , 
   contracts.plan_id ,
   contracts.status ,
   contracts.first_payment_date ,
   contracts.management 
FROM {{ ref('proc_closure_contracts') }} AS contracts
)

, clouser_subs as (
SELECT 
   -- Contracts Info
   contracts.id AS contract_id ,
   contracts.status AS contract_status , 
   coalesce( (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, contracts.first_payment_date)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE, subscription.payment_date::DATE) AS contract_first_payment_date_local , 
   (timezone( 'UTC', contracts.first_payment_date)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE AS contract_first_payment_date_utc , 
   plans.has_management AS contracts_has_management , 
   -- Subs Info
   subscription.id AS sub_id ,
   coalesce( (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, subscription.payment_date)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE, subscription.payment_date::DATE) AS sub_payment_date_local , 
   (timezone( 'UTC', subscription.payment_date)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE AS sub_payment_date_utc , 
   subscription.property_id , 
   prop_mz.geo_id , 
   subscription.init_reason AS sub_init_reason ,
   -- Plans info
   plans.id AS plan_id ,
   plans.name AS plan_name , 
   plans.description AS plan_description , 
   plans.has_management  AS plan_has_management 
FROM {{ ref('stg_subscription_subscription') }} AS subscription 
LEFT JOIN contracts_clean AS contracts 
        ON contracts.id =  subscription.contract_id
LEFT JOIN plans_clean AS plans
        ON plans.id = contracts.plan_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz 
        ON prop_mz.property_id = subscription.property_id
)

SELECT *
FROM clouser_subs

    created_at,

    length(clean_body) as clean_body_characters,
    audit_id,
    author_id,
    ticket_id

						when '1. Chile' then 'Chile'
						when '2. Colombia' then 'Colombia'
						when '3. México' then 'Mexico'
					end) 
		as country,
		coalesce(proc_properties_macrozone.region) as region,
		coalesce(proc_properties_macrozone.City_Houm,case 
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Envigado' then 'Medellín'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Región Metropolitana' then 'Santiago'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Estado de México' then 'Ciudad de México'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Quilpue' then 'Viña del Mar'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Región de Valparaiso' then 'V Región Costa'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Buin' then 'Santiago'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Cundinamarca' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Soacha' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Otro' then null
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Chicureo' then 'Santiago'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Bello' then 'Medellín'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Región del Biobío' then 'Región Bío Bío'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Paine' then 'Santiago'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Madrid' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Calera de Tango' then 'Santiago'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Itagüi' then 'Medellín'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Chía' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Limache' then 'Valparaiso'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Mosquera' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Cajicá' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Funza' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Cota' then 'Bogotá'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Valparaiso' then 'V Region Costa'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Itagüí' then 'Medellín'
													when proc_deals.city_2 = 'Concepción' then 'Región Bío Bío'
												else proc_deals.city_2 end
								) as city,
		coalesce(proc_properties_macrozone.supply_source, proc_deals.supply_source) as supply_source,
		case
			when funnel = '1. Supply' then qualification 
			when funnel = '2. Demand' then buyer_qualification 
			else null
		end as lead_qualification,
		coalesce(case when proc_deals.business like '%ianza%' then 'Brokers' else null end,
						proc_properties_macrozone.supply_relation) as supply_relation,
		proc_deals.business
	from {{ref('proc_tmp_supply_deals')}} proc_deals
	left join {{ref('proc_tmp_supply_properties_macrozone')}} proc_properties_macrozone on proc_deals.property_id = proc_properties_macrozone.property_id
)
, second_clean as (
	select 
		first_clean.deal_id,
		first_clean.property_id,
		first_clean.original_date,
		first_clean.country,
		case
			when first_clean.region is null then
				case
					when first_clean.city is null then
						case --Arreglo para asignar leads a regiones, necesario mejorar (TD) ya sea operacionalmente o con otra fuente de información.
							when first_clean.country = 'Chile' then 'Región Metropolitana'
							when first_clean.country = 'Colombia' then 'Bogotá, D.C & Cundinamarca'
							when first_clean.country = 'Mexico' then 'Ciudad de México'
							else null
						end
					else dim_cities.region_houm
				end
			else first_clean.region
		end as region,
		coalesce(first_clean.city,	case --Mismo punto anterior, Technical Debt por mejorar.
										when country = 'Chile' then 'Santiago'
										when country = 'Colombia' then 'Bogotá'
										when country = 'Mexico' then 'Ciudad de México'
										else null 
									end) as city, 
		business,
		first_clean.supply_source,
		case
			when first_clean.country = 'Colombia' and lead_qualification = 6 then 'New Properties'
			else coalesce(first_clean.supply_relation,'Landlord') --Validar comercialmente si definicion es util
		end as supply_relation,
		first_clean.lead_qualification
	from first_clean
	left join {{ref('proc_tmp_supply_cities')}} dim_cities on first_clean.city = dim_cities.City_Houm)
select
	second_clean.deal_id,
	second_clean.property_id,
	second_clean.original_date as original_time, --La hora original esta en UTC
	timezone(dim_cities.timezone, timezone('UTC',second_clean.original_date)) as local_time,
	second_clean.country,
	second_clean.region,
	second_clean.city,
	second_clean.business,
	second_clean.supply_source,
	second_clean.supply_relation,
	second_clean.lead_qualification,
	proc_deals.person_id,
	proc_deals.qualification_date,
	proc_deals.funnel
from second_clean
left join {{ref('proc_tmp_supply_cities')}} dim_cities on dim_cities.City_Houm = second_clean.city
left join {{ref('proc_tmp_supply_deals')}} proc_deals on proc_deals.id = second_clean.deal_id

model.houm.proc_supply_schedules.raw_sql:
Select
    schedules.id        schedule_id 
    , prop_mz.geo_id
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.created_at)::timestamp with time zone)::date created_at
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.begin_date)::timestamp with time zone)::date begin_date
    , schedules.prop_id property_id 
    , properties.supply_source
    , properties.supply_relation
    , schedules.status
    , scheduler_scheduletypes.name as schedule_type_name
    , applicant.email
    , applicant.id as  applicant_id 
from {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedules') }} AS schedules
    left join {{ ref('stg_scheduler_scheduletypes') }} AS scheduler_scheduletypes on scheduler_scheduletypes.id  = schedules.schedule_type_id
    left join {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedulehasapplicant') }} AS scheduler_schedulehasapplicant  on scheduler_schedulehasapplicant.schedule_id     = schedules.id 
    left join {{ ref('stg_arriendoasegurado_applicant') }} AS applicant on applicant.id = scheduler_schedulehasapplicant.applicant_id
    left join {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }} AS prop_mz  on prop_mz.property_id = schedules.prop_id 
    left join {{ ref('proc_properties') }} as properties on properties.id = schedules.prop_id
where scheduler_scheduletypes.name in ('Photo','SalesPhoto')

model.houm.proc_tmp_supply_persons_email.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

with emails as(
	SELECT 
		DISTINCT deals.person_id.value::integer AS person_id, 
		e_email.value::text AS email, 
		e_email.primary::boolean AS primary_email 
	FROM 
		{{ref('stg_deals')}} AS deals, 
		deals.person_id.email AS e_email 
	ORDER BY 1
)
SELECT 
	ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY emails.person_id ASC) AS id, 
	emails.person_id AS person_id, 
	case 
		when length(emails.email) < 1 then null
		else emails.email
	end AS email, 
	emails.primary_email AS primary_email 
FROM emails
ORDER BY 1

						deals.user_id.value::integer as user_id,
						deals.value, 
						deals.currency, 
						deals.add_time, 
						deals.update_time, 
						deals.active, 
						deals.deleted, 
						deals.status, 
						deals.next_activity_date, 
						deals.next_activity_time, 
						deals.next_activity_id, 
						deals.last_activity_date, 
						deals.lost_reason, 
						deals.pipeline_id, 
						deals.won_time, 
						deals.first_won_time, 
						deals.lost_time, 
						deals.email_messages_count, 
						deals.activities_count, 
						deals.done_activities_count, 
						deals.undone_activities_count, 
						deals.expected_close_date, 
						deals."label", 
						deals.person_name, 
						deals.org_name, 
						deals.owner_name, 
						deals."29983ea0d395dd72390c71a1bd76c80546609761" AS property_link, 
						deals."79f08ab8c03c88c6bf3148119778d7f64f833a41" AS property_address, 
						case deals."408ab88af9150b9bb785f1453bd42bc4a1eb5f07"
							when 81 then '0'
							when 82 then '1'
							when 83 then '2'
							when 84 then '3'
							when 85 then '4'
							when 86 then '5'
							else "408ab88af9150b9bb785f1453bd42bc4a1eb5f07"
						end AS qualification, 
						deals."91ae7d54bd0239721db388ee0c0ffbee7a68d249" AS email,
						deals."b224b2df6dddae4a3f59d9ab92496c84fb81fcff" AS phone, 
						deals."c116f72d816aa5ce9f2a925345b364775a3933ac" AS property_type, 
						deals."76d94f6699c815a28f47ea500f2481fa7aede96c" AS source, 
						deals."d5b32c860fba2502a7d0ef77db7f93985d5dbfbb" AS city, 
						case deals."6dd9993bf1db83c740ad3bcffee5fd8143f5fad9"
							when 107 then 'Rental'
							when 110 then 'Sales'
							else "6dd9993bf1db83c740ad3bcffee5fd8143f5fad9"::text
						end AS pipedrive_business, 
						deals."aebaba770d785ee2eb0847592ed4ee2cc468de21" AS property_id, 
						deals."be6579db0f5918a46f43181eec54056ca8354a50" AS able_for_ep, 
						deals."853838575c80f1c1f80117953412998c0ea935ad" AS deal_country,
						deals."16d9ee32ae9b3d34a0c69317871b2d3c612a69ed" AS country,
						deals."76eb4b457cf491efd1de1cfcaf9ea2da37c23b36"::date AS qualification_date,
						case deals."d94ddd002dfe910eb5a72673bcc54b1789d21384" 
							when 116 then 'Crédito pre-aprobado' 
				            when 114 then 'Todo al contado'
				            when 193 then 'Subsidio habitacional'
				            when '116,117' then 'Crédito pre-aprobado/Sin financiamiento'
				            when 115 then 'Crédito aprobado'
				            when 117 then 'Sin financiamiento'
				            when '114,115' then 'Todo al contado/Crédito aprobado'
				            when '114,117' then 'Todo al contado/Sin financiamiento'
				            when 207 then 'No quiere detallar'
				            when '114,193' then 'Todo al contado/Subsidio habitacional'
				            when '115,193' then 'Crédito aprobado/Subsidio habitacional'
				            when '116,193' then 'Crédito pre-aprobado/Subsidio habitacional'
				        	else "d94ddd002dfe910eb5a72673bcc54b1789d21384"::text
						end AS funding,
						case deals."285678337a5c71fc5ce67cb47fd0c983d5fd4576" 
							when 118 then 'Inversión'

model.houm.proc_macrozone.raw_sql:
Select 
    id geo_id 
	, created_at
	, updated_at
	, name
	, description
    , country
	, city
	, city_marketplace_id
    , polygon 
    , timezone
    , case  when country = 'Chile' then 'CL' when country = 'Colombia' then 'CO' when country in ('Mexico', 'México')  then 'MX'
            else 'NA' 
    end country_sufix
    --, city
    , case 
    	when  a.city in ('Santiago','Buin','Calera de Tango','Chicureo','Paine')    then 'Región Metropolitana'
    	when  a.city in ('Valparaíso','Viña del Mar','Limache','Quilpué')   		then 'V Región'
    	when  a.city = 'Concepción'   								then 'Región Bío Bío'
    	when  a.city in ('Bogotá','Cundinamarca')   				then 'Bogotá, D.C & Cundinamarca' 
    	when  a.city in ('Medellín','Medellin Oriente') 			then 'Provincia de Medellín'
    	when  a.city = 'Ciudad de México' 							then 'Ciudad de México'
    	when  a.city = 'Guadalajara' 								then 'Guadalajara'
    	when  a.city = 'Monterrey' 									then 'Monterrey'
    	when  a.city = 'Tijuana' 						    		then 'Tijuana'
    	else 'Null'                                                 end Region_Houm
    , case 
				when  a.city = 'Santiago' 									    then 'Santiago'
				when  a.city in ('Buin','Calera de Tango','Chicureo','Paine')	then 'Santiago Periferia'
				when  a.city in ('Valparaíso','Viña del Mar')   				then 'V Región Costa'
				when  a.city in ('Limache','Quilpué')   						then 'V Región Interior'
				when  a.city = 'Concepción'   								then 'Región Bío Bío'
				when  a.id in (14,15,16,17,18) 								then 'Bogotá'
				when  a.id in (24,25,61,66,65,63,62,64) 					then 'Bogotá Periferia'
				when  a.city = 'Medellín' 									then 'Medellín'
				when  a.city = 'Medellin Oriente' 							then 'Medellin Oriente'
				when  a.city = 'Ciudad de México' 							then 'Ciudad de México'
				when  a.city = 'Guadalajara' 								then 'Guadalajara'
				when  a.city = 'Monterrey' 									then 'Monterrey'
				when  a.city = 'Tijuana' 									then 'Tijuana'
				else 'Null'                                                 end City_Houm
from {{ ref('stg_macrozone') }} as a

model.houm.proc_properties.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

select a.id
		,a.created_at
		,a.updated_at
		,a.first_publication_date
		,a.last_publication_date
        ,CASE   when for_rental = True and  for_sale = True then 'Rental & Sale'
                        when for_rental = True and for_sale = False then 'Rental'
                        when for_rental = False and for_sale = True then 'Sale'
                        end as business_type
		, CASE  WHEN b.role::text in ('property_broker','real_estate_developer') or  b.id = 60441 THEN 'B2B'
            			ELSE 'B2C'
      					END AS supply_source 
    	, CASE  WHEN b.role = 'property_broker' or  b.id = 60441 THEN 'Brokers'
            			WHEN b.role = 'real_estate_developer' then 'New Properties'
           				WHEN length( b.referral_id) = 5 then 'Partners'
            			ELSE 'Landlord'
      					END AS supply_relation
		,a.neighborhood_id

model.houm.proc_tmp_supply_persons_phone.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

with phones as (
SELECT 
	DISTINCT deals.person_id.value::integer AS person_id, 
	e_phone.value::text AS phone, 
	e_phone.primary::boolean AS primary_phone 
FROM 
	{{ref('stg_deals')}} AS deals, 
	deals.person_id.phone AS e_phone 
)
SELECT 
	ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY phones.person_id ASC) AS id, 
	phones.person_id AS person_id, 
	case 
		when length(phones.phone)<1 then null 
		else phones.phone 
	end AS phone, 
	phones.primary_phone AS primary_phone 
FROM phones 
ORDER BY 1 DESC

order by 1 desc

with macrozone as (
    select
        property_id,
        min(proc_macrozone.geo_id) as geo_id,
        max(proc_macrozone.timezone) as timezone
    from
        {{ref('proc_propertydetails')}}
    left join
        {{ref('proc_macrozone')}} on (ST_Contains(proc_macrozone.polygon,ST_SetSRID(ST_Point(proc_propertydetails.longitud, proc_propertydetails.latitud), 4326)) = true)
    group by 1
), first_clean as (
select 
    proc_properties.id as property_id,
    proc_properties.created_at,
    proc_properties.first_publication_date, 
    proc_macrozone.country,
    proc_macrozone.Region_Houm as region, 
    proc_macrozone.City_Houm,
    macrozone.timezone,
    macrozone.geo_id,
    proc_properties.business_type as business,
    proc_properties.supply_source,
    proc_properties.supply_relation
from {{ ref('proc_properties') }}
left join macrozone on macrozone.property_id = proc_properties.id
left join {{ ref('proc_macrozone') }} on proc_macrozone.geo_id = macrozone.geo_id
order by proc_properties.created_at desc
)
select *,
    timezone(first_clean.timezone,first_clean.first_publication_date) as local_first_publication_date
from first_clean

{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH google_campaign AS (
SELECT
    'Google' AS platform ,
    campaign_id ,
    campaign_name  
FROM {{ ref('stg_paid_media_google_campaign_keys') }} 
)

, facebook_campaign AS (
SELECT
    'Facebook' AS platform ,
    campaign_id ,
    campaign_name  
FROM {{ ref('stg_paid_media_facebook_campaign_keys') }} 
)

, paid_media_campaign AS (
SELECT 
    *
FROM  google_campaign
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
    * 
From facebook_campaign
)

, campaign_business AS (
SELECT 
    campaign_id ,
    campaign_name , 
    platform , 
    CASE
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Sales%' THEN 'Seller'
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Rentals%' THEN 'Landlord'
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%New Properties%' THEN 'Buyer New Properties'
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Buyers%' THEN 'Buyer Second Hand'
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Tenants%' THEN 'Tenant'
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Branding%' THEN 'Branding'
        ELSE 'Branding' END AS business_marketing ,  
    CASE
        WHEN (campaign_name LIKE '%Sales%' OR campaign_name LIKE '%Rentals%') THEN 'Supply'
        WHEN (campaign_name LIKE '%Buyers%' OR campaign_name LIKE '%Tenants%') THEN 'Demand'
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Branding%' THEN 'Branding'
    ELSE 'Branding' END funnel_marketing , 
    CASE
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Medellín%' THEN 31::int
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Bogotá%' THEN 14::int 
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Región Metropolitana%' THEN 79::int
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Valparaíso%' THEN  11::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Concepción%' THEN 8::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Ciudad de México%' THEN 19::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Monterrey%' THEN 54::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Tijuana%' THEN 67::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Guadalajara%' THEN 30::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Puebla%' THEN 19::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%Querétaro%' THEN 19::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%GDL%' THEN  30::INT
        WHEN campaign_name LIKE '%CDMX%' THEN 19::INT
        ELSE NULL END AS geo_id  
FROM paid_media_campaign
)

SELECT 
    campaign_business.campaign_id ,
    campaign_business.platform , 
    campaign_business.campaign_name , 
    dim_geo.country , 
    dim_geo.Region_Houm ,
    dim_geo.City_Houm ,
    dim_geo.geo_id , 
    campaign_business.business_marketing ,
    campaign_business.funnel_marketing  
FROM campaign_business
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('dim_macrozones') }} AS dim_geo 
    ON dim_geo.geo_id = campaign_business.geo_id

WITH google_cl AS (
SELECT 
    'Google' AS platform ,
    campaign_name , 
    executed_at , 
    'USD'::TEXT AS currency , 
    CASE  
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2021-07-01'::DATE AND '2022-07-31'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/764.15::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2021-08-01'::DATE AND '2022-08-31'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/798.21::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2021-09-01'::DATE AND '2022-09-30'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/813.90::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2021-10-01'::DATE AND '2022-10-31'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/852.495::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2021-11-01'::DATE AND '2022-11-30'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/851.456::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2021-12-01'::DATE AND '2022-12-31'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/879.43::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2022-01-01'::DATE AND '2022-04-30'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/850::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2022-05-01'::DATE AND '2022-05-31'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/860::FLOAT
        WHEN executed_at BETWEEN '2022-06-01'::DATE AND '2022-08-01'::DATE THEN day_cost::FLOAT/890::FLOAT
    ELSE day_cost::float/usd_cl.valor::float END day_cost ,
    day_clicks , 
    day_impressions
FROM {{ ref('stg_paid_media_google_campaigns_cl') }} AS proc_google_cl 
LEFT JOIN economic_indicator_dolar AS usd_cl 
    ON usd_cl.fecha  = proc_google_cl.executed_at 
WHERE executed_at >= '2021-07-01'::DATE
)

WHERE executed_at >= '2021-07-01'::DATE
)

    union_platform.day_impressions   
FROM union_platform
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('proc_marketing_paid_media_campaign') }} AS campaign_id 
    ON campaign_id.campaign_name = union_platform.campaign_name
)

SELECT *

model.houm.sales_local_revenue.raw_sql:
WITH localsalesrevenue AS (
    SELECT
        country,
        DATE_TRUNC(
            'month',
            promise_date
        ) :: DATE AS date_month,
        SUM(
            local_amount *(
                sales_revenue.seller_commission + sales_revenue.buyer_commission
            ) 
        ) as amount
    FROM
        payments.sales_revenue
    GROUP BY
        2,
        country
)
SELECT
        'sales_transactions' AS metric,'local_revenue' AS col,*
FROM
    localsalesrevenue

model.houm.proc_cx_nps_new_listing.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH nps_whatsapp AS (
    SELECT 
        CASE
            WHEN nps."timestamp" IS NULL OR nps."timestamp"::text = ''::character varying::text THEN '2021-10-01'::date
            ELSE "left"(nps."timestamp"::text, 10)::date
        END AS date,
        CASE
            WHEN nps."timestamp" IS NULL OR nps."timestamp"::text = ''::character varying::text THEN '00:00:00'::time without time zone
            ELSE "left"("right"(nps."timestamp"::text, 9), 8)::time without time zone
        END AS "time",
        CASE
            WHEN nps.recommendation IN (9,10) THEN 100::numeric(18, 0)
               WHEN nps.recommendation IN (7,8) THEN 0.00
               WHEN nps.recommendation IN (0,6) THEN - 100::numeric(18, 0)
               ELSE NULL
        END AS nps,
        nps.name,
        nps.phone,
        nps."role",
        nps.country,
        nps."timestamp",
        CASE
            WHEN nps.source = 1 THEN '1.Publicidad'
            WHEN nps.source = 2 THEN '2.Google'
            WHEN nps.source = 3 THEN '3.Me lo recomendaron'
            WHEN nps.source = 4 THEN '4.Redes sociales'
            WHEN nps.source = 5 THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN nps.source = 6 THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source,
           nps.process_quickness,
           nps.process_clarity,
           nps.recommendation,
           nps.comments,
           case when role like '%rent%' then 'Rentals'
           		when role like '%sale%' then 'Sales'
           	else null end as business,
           	property_id
    FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_rentas_new_listing')}} nps
    ),
nps_survicate AS (
    SELECT 
        left(first_response_date, 10)::date AS date,
        right(first_response_date, 8)::time AS time,
        nps * 100 AS nps,
        '' AS name,
        '' AS phone,
        'rent_propietary_listing' AS role,
        country,
        first_response_date::character varying,
        CASE
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Publicidad' THEN '1.Publicidad'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Googleando' THEN '2.Google'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Me lo recomendaron' THEN '3.Me lo recomendaron'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Redes sociales' THEN '4.Redes sociales'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'De un portal de propiedades' THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Otro' THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source,
        CASE m1_process_speed
            WHEN 'Muy satisfecho' THEN '10'
            WHEN 'Satisfecho' THEN '8'
            WHEN 'Neutro' THEN '6'
            WHEN 'Insatisfecho' THEN '4'
            WHEN 'Muy insatisfecho' THEN '2'
            ELSE null
        END AS process_quickness,
        CASE m1_information_clarity
            WHEN 'Muy satisfecho' THEN '10'
            WHEN 'Satisfecho' THEN '8'
            WHEN 'Neutro' THEN '6'
            WHEN 'Insatisfecho' THEN '4'
            WHEN 'Muy insatisfecho' THEN '2'
            ELSE null
        END AS process_clarity,
        nps_service_recommendation,
        CASE
            when text1_bad_answer = '' then
                case
                    when text1_neutral_answer = '' then
                            case
                                when text1_good_answer = '' then ''
                                else 'Good: ' || text1_good_answer end
                    else 'Neutral: ' || text1_neutral_answer end
            else 'Bad: ' || text1_bad_answer || ' Neutral: ' || text1_neutral_answer || ' Good: ' || text1_good_answer 
        END AS comments,
        null as business,
        null as property_id
    FROM {{ref('stg_survicate_nps_landlord_listing')}} AS nps
    WHERE nps.first_response_date::date <= '2021-10-27'
    )
SELECT 
    * 
FROM 
    nps_whatsapp
UNION ALL
SELECT
    * 
FROM 
    nps_survicate
ORDER BY 1 DESC, 2 DESC

model.houm.proc_cx_nps_visit_done.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH scheduler_schedules AS (
	SELECT 
		schedule_id as id,
		appraiser_id 
	FROM {{ref('proc_tmp_demand_schedules_cleaned')}} hss 
),
scheduler_appraisers AS (
	SELECT 
		id,
		name 
	FROM {{ref('stg_scheduler_appraisers')}} 
), 
raw_nps_whatsapp as (
	SELECT 
		appraiser, 
		schedule_id::integer, 
		property_id::integer, 
		to_date("date",'DD/MM/YYYY') as "date",
		"time"::time without time zone, 
		address,
		CASE houmer_service
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			ELSE houmer_service::integer
		END as houmer_service,
		CASE houmer_knowledge
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			ELSE houmer_knowledge::integer
		END as houmer_knowledge,
		CASE schedule_easyness 
			WHEN '-' then null
			ELSE schedule_easyness::integer
		END as schedule_easyness,
		CASE visit_success 
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			else cast(visit_success as integer) end as visit_success,
		CASE recommendation 
			WHEN '-' THEN null
			ELSE recommendation::integer
		END as recommendation,
		country,
		business,
		comments
	FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_visits_done')}}
),
nps_whatsapp AS (
SELECT 
    scheduler_appraisers.name AS appraiser, 
    q.schedule_id,
	q.property_id,
	q.date,
    q.time,
    q.address,
    q.recommendation,
    q.country,
    q.business,
    q.comments, 
    CASE
        WHEN q.recommendation IN (9,10) THEN 100
		WHEN q.recommendation IN (7,8) THEN 0.00
		WHEN q.recommendation IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN -100
		ELSE null 
	END AS NPS,
	houmer_service,
	houmer_knowledge,
	schedule_easyness AS schedule_easiness,
	visit_success
FROM raw_nps_whatsapp AS q
LEFT JOIN scheduler_schedules ON scheduler_schedules.id = q.schedule_id
LEFT JOIN scheduler_appraisers ON scheduler_appraisers.id = scheduler_schedules.appraiser_id
ORDER BY "date" ASC, "time" ASC
),
nps_survicate AS (
	SELECT 		
		'' as appraiser ,
		null::integer as schedule_id,
		null::integer as property_id,
		"left"(nps.first_response_date::text, 10)::date AS date, 
		"right"(nps.first_response_date::text, 8)::time without time zone AS "time", 
		'' as address,
		nps.nps_service_recommendation::integer AS nps_service_recommendation, 
		nps.country, 
		'' as business, 
        CASE
        	WHEN nps.text1_bad_answer = '' THEN 
                CASE
                    WHEN nps.text1_neutral_answer = '' THEN 
                    	CASE
                        	WHEN nps.text1_good_answer = '' THEN ''
                        	ELSE 'Good: ' || nps.text1_good_answer
                    	END
                    ELSE 'Neutral: ' || nps.text1_neutral_answer
                END
            ELSE (((('Bad: ' || nps.text1_bad_answer) || ' Neutral: ') || nps.text1_neutral_answer) || ' Good: ') || nps.text1_good_answer
        END AS comments,
        nps.nps * 100 AS nps, 
        null AS houmer_service, 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Muy de acuerdo'::text THEN 10
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'De acuerdo'::text THEN 8
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Neutro'::text THEN 6
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Desacuerdo'::text THEN 4
            WHEN nps.m1_houmer_delivers_info::text = 'Muy en desacuerdo'::text THEN 2
            ELSE null
        END AS houmer_knowledge, 
        CASE
        	WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Muy de acuerdo' THEN 10
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'De acuerdo' THEN 8
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Neutro' THEN 6
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Desacuerdo' THEN 4
            WHEN nps.m1_schedule_easiness::text = 'Muy en desacuerdo' THEN 2
        	ELSE null
        END AS schedule_easiness,
        null as visit_success
    FROM {{ref('stg_survicate_nps_visit_done')}} nps
    WHERE nps.first_response_date::date <= '2021-10-24'::date
	)
SELECT * 
FROM nps_whatsapp
UNION ALL
SELECT * 
FROM nps_survicate

with nps_whatsapp_raw as (
    select 
        appraiser, 
        schedule_id, 
		case trim(property_id)
			when '-' then null
			else cast(property_id as integer) 
		end as property_id,
        to_date(np."date",'DD/MM/YYYY') as date, 
        np."time"::time, 
        address,
		case trim(houmer_service)
			when '-' then null
			else cast(houmer_service as integer) end as houmer_service,
		case trim(houmer_knowledge)
			when '-' then null
			else cast(houmer_knowledge as integer) end as houmer_knowledge,
		case trim(schedule_easyness) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(schedule_easyness as integer) end as schedule_easyness,
		case trim(visit_success) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(visit_success as integer) end as visit_success,
		case trim(recommendation) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(recommendation as integer) end as recommendation,
		country, 
		comments
    from {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_photo')}} np
),
nps_whatsapp as (
    select 
        nps_whatsapp_raw.*,
        hss.business,
		case when recommendation in (9,10) then 100
			when recommendation in (7,8) then 0.00
			when recommendation in (1,2,3,4,5,6) then -100
			else null end as NPS
    from nps_whatsapp_raw
    left join {{ref('proc_tmp_demand_schedules_cleaned')}} hss on hss.schedule_id = nps_whatsapp_raw.schedule_id
),
nps_survicate as ( 
    select 
        null as appraiser, 
        null as schedule_id, 
        null as property_id,
        left(first_response_date,10)::date as date, 
        right(first_response_date,8)::time as time,
        null as address,
        m1_houmer_during_visit*2 as houmer_service,
        m1_houmer_before_visit*2 as houmer_knowledge,
        m1_website_simplicity*2 as schedule_easyness,
        case property_photos_experience when 'Extremely happy' then 10
            when 'Happy' then 8
            when 'Neutral' then 6
            when 'Unsatisfied' then 4
            when 'Extremely unsatisfied' then 2
            else null
        end as visit_success,
        null as recommendation,
        country,
        case when text1_bad_answer = '' then case when text1_neutral_answer = '' then '' else text1_neutral_answer end else 'Bad:'||text1_bad_answer || ' Neutral: '|| text1_neutral_answer end as comments,

)

    *

		case trim(visit_success) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(visit_success as integer) end as visit_success,
		case trim(recommendation) 
			when '-' then null
			else cast(recommendation as integer) end as recommendation,
		country, 
		comments
    from "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_whatsapp_nps_photo" np
),
nps_whatsapp as (
    select 
        nps_whatsapp_raw.*,
        hss.business,
		case when recommendation in (9,10) then 100
			when recommendation in (7,8) then 0.00
			when recommendation in (1,2,3,4,5,6) then -100
			else null end as NPS
    from nps_whatsapp_raw
    left join "houmdw_prod"."dbt_processing"."proc_tmp_demand_schedules_cleaned" hss on hss.schedule_id = nps_whatsapp_raw.schedule_id
),
nps_survicate as ( 
    select 
        null as appraiser, 
        null as schedule_id, 
        null as property_id,
        left(first_response_date,10)::date as date, 
        right(first_response_date,8)::time as time,
        null as address,
        m1_houmer_during_visit*2 as houmer_service,
        m1_houmer_before_visit*2 as houmer_knowledge,
        m1_website_simplicity*2 as schedule_easyness,
        case property_photos_experience when 'Extremely happy' then 10
            when 'Happy' then 8
            when 'Neutral' then 6
            when 'Unsatisfied' then 4
            when 'Extremely unsatisfied' then 2
            else null
        end as visit_success,
        null as recommendation,
        country,
        case when text1_bad_answer = '' then case when text1_neutral_answer = '' then '' else text1_neutral_answer end else 'Bad:'||text1_bad_answer || ' Neutral: '|| text1_neutral_answer end as comments,
        '' as business,
        nps*100 as nps
    from "houmdw_prod"."dbt_staging"."stg_survicate_nps_photo_done" 
    where date < '2021-10-21'
)
SELECT 
    * 
FROM 
    nps_whatsapp
UNION ALL
SELECT
    * 
FROM 
    nps_survicate
ORDER BY "date" DESC, "time" DESC

            WHEN nps.recommendation::text = 7::character varying::text OR nps.recommendation::text = 8::character varying::text THEN 0.00
            WHEN nps.recommendation::text = 1::character varying::text OR nps.recommendation::text = 2::character varying::text OR nps.recommendation::text = 3::character varying::text OR nps.recommendation::text = 4::character varying::text OR nps.recommendation::text = 5::character varying::text OR nps.recommendation::text = 6::character varying::text THEN - 100::numeric::numeric(18,0)
            ELSE NULL::numeric::numeric(18,0)
        END AS nps, nps.name, nps.phone, nps."role", nps.property_id, nps.subscription_id, nps.country, nps."timestamp", 
        case nps.attention_satisfaction when '-' then null::integer else nps.attention_satisfaction::integer end, 
        case nps.problem_solving when '-' then null::integer else nps.problem_solving::integer end as problem_solving_conditions, 
        case nps.recommendation when '-' then null::integer else nps.recommendation::integer end as recommendation, 
        nps.comments
    FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_automatic_tenants')}} nps order by date asc
   ), nps_survicate as(
   select "left"(nps.first_response_date::text, 10)::date AS date, 
		"right"(nps.first_response_date::text, 8)::time without time zone AS "time",
		nps*100 as nps,
		'' as name,
		'' as phone,
		'tenant_24_hrs' as role,
		null as property_id,
        null as subscription_id,
		country,
		first_response_date::text as "timestamp",
		CASE
            WHEN nps.houmer_service_satisfaction::text = 'Extremely happy'::text THEN 10::integer
            WHEN nps.houmer_service_satisfaction::text = 'Happy'::text THEN 8::integer
            WHEN nps.houmer_service_satisfaction::text = 'Neutro'::text THEN 6::integer
            WHEN nps.houmer_service_satisfaction::text = 'Unsatisfied'::text THEN 4::integer
            WHEN nps.houmer_service_satisfaction::text = 'Extremely unsatisfied'::text THEN 2::integer
            ELSE null::integer
        END AS attention_satisfaction,
        case nps.expected_property_status when 'Sí' then 10
        									when 'No' then 4
        									when 'Con algunos detalles' then 8
        									else null end as problem_solving_conditions,
        nps.nps_service_recommendation::integer as recommendation,
                        CASE
                    WHEN nps.text1_bad_answer::text = ''::text THEN 
                    CASE
                        WHEN nps.text1_neutral_answer::text = ''::text THEN 
                        CASE
                            WHEN nps.text1_good_answer::text = ''::text THEN ''::text
                            ELSE 'Good: '::text || nps.text1_good_answer::text
                        END
                        ELSE 'Neutral: '::text || nps.text1_neutral_answer::text
                    END
                    ELSE (((('Bad: '::text || nps.text1_bad_answer::text) || ' Neutral: '::text) || nps.text1_neutral_answer::text) || ' Good: '::text) || nps.text1_good_answer::text
                END AS comments
	from survicate.nps_tenant_satisfaction_24hrs nps
   )
   select * from nps_whatsapp
   union all
   select * from nps_survicate

WITH nps_whatsapp AS (
	SELECT 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.answered_at IS NULL OR nps.answered_at = '' THEN '2021-10-25'::date
            ELSE left(nps.answered_at, 10)::date
        END AS "date", 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.answered_at IS NULL OR nps.answered_at = '' THEN '00:00:00'::time without time zone
            ELSE left(right(nps.answered_at, 9), 8)::time without time zone
        END AS "time", 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.recommendation in (9,10) THEN 100

            ELSE NULL
        END AS nps, 
		nps.name, 
		nps.phone, 
		nps."role",

		nps.answered_at::timestamp,

			WHEN nps.property_id ='-' THEN null
			ELSE nps.property_id::integer
		END AS property_id, 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.source = 1 THEN '1.Publicidad'
            WHEN nps.source = 2 THEN '2.Google'
            WHEN nps.source = 3 THEN '3.Me lo recomendaron'
            WHEN nps.source = 4 THEN '4.Redes sociales'
            WHEN nps.source = 5 THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN nps.source = 6 THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source, 
		CASE
			WHEN left(contract_signature,1) BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN nps.contract_signature::integer
			ELSE NULL
		END AS contract_signature,
		CASE
			WHEN left(nps.recommendation,1) BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN nps.recommendation::integer
			ELSE NULL
		END AS recommendation,
		nps.comments

		'' AS phone,

		first_response_date::timestamp,
		null AS property_id,

            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Publicidad' THEN '1.Publicidad'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Googleando' THEN '2.Google'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Me lo recomendaron' THEN '3.Me lo recomendaron'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Redes sociales' THEN '4.Redes sociales'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'De un portal de propiedades' THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'
            WHEN sc1_customer_source = 'Otro' THEN '6.Otro'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS source,
        CASE m1_contract_signing_easiness 
			WHEN 'Muy de acuerdo' THEN 10
        	WHEN 'De acuerdo' THEN 8
        	WHEN 'Neutro' THEN 6
        	WHEN 'Desacuerdo' THEN 4
        	WHEN 'Muy en desacuerdo' THEN 2
        	ELSE null
        END AS contract_signature,
        nps_service_recommendation,
        CASE 
			WHEN text1_bad_answer = '' THEN

        				CASE 
							WHEN text1_good_answer = '' THEN ''
        					ELSE 'Good: '||text1_good_answer
						END
        			ELSE 'Neutral: '||text1_neutral_answer 
				END 
        	ELSE 'Bad: '||text1_bad_answer || ' Neutral: '|| text1_neutral_answer||' Good: '||text1_good_answer 
		END AS comments

            WHEN nps.sc1_customer_source::text = 'De un portal de propiedades'::character varying::text THEN '5.De un portal de propiedades'::character varying
            WHEN nps.sc1_customer_source::text = 'Otro'::character varying::text THEN '6.Otro'::character varying

            WHEN nps.m1_answer_speed::text = 'De acuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '8'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_answer_speed::text = 'Neutro'::character varying::text THEN '6'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_answer_speed::text = 'Desacuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '4'::character varying

            WHEN nps.m1_contract_signing_easiness::text = 'De acuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '8'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_contract_signing_easiness::text = 'Neutro'::character varying::text THEN '6'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_contract_signing_easiness::text = 'Desacuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '4'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_contract_signing_easiness::text = 'Muy en desacuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '2'::character varying
            ELSE NULL::character varying
        END AS contract_signature, 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.m1_payment_easiness::text = 'Muy de acuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '10'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_payment_easiness::text = 'De acuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '8'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_payment_easiness::text = 'Neutro'::character varying::text THEN '6'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_payment_easiness::text = 'Desacuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '4'::character varying
            WHEN nps.m1_payment_easiness::text = 'Muy en desacuerdo'::character varying::text THEN '2'::character varying
            ELSE NULL::character varying
        END AS payment_easiness, nps.nps_service_recommendation::character varying AS nps_service_recommendation, 
        CASE
            WHEN nps.text1_bad_answer::text = ''::character varying::text THEN 
                CASE
                    WHEN nps.text1_neutral_answer::text = ''::character varying::text THEN 
                        CASE
                            WHEN nps.text1_good_answer::text = ''::character varying::text THEN ''::character varying::text
                            ELSE 'Good: '::character varying::text || nps.text1_good_answer::text
                        END
                    ELSE 'Neutral: '::character varying::text || nps.text1_neutral_answer::text
                END
            ELSE (((('Bad: '::character varying::text || nps.text1_bad_answer::text) || ' Neutral: '::character varying::text) || nps.text1_neutral_answer::text) || ' Good: '::character varying::text) || nps.text1_good_answer::text
        END AS comments
    FROM {{ref('stg_survicate_nps_tenant_new_sub')}} nps
    WHERE nps.first_response_date::date <= '2021-10-24'::date
)
SELECT *
FROM nps_whatsapp
UNION ALL

FROM nps_survicate
ORDER BY 1 DESC

model.houm.proc_cx_nps_visit_cancelled.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH nps_visits_cancelled AS (
	SELECT 
        address,
		country,
		comments,
		appraiser,
		visit_type,
		schedule_id,
		property_id,
		(split_part(begin_date,'-',3)||'-'||split_part(begin_date,'-',2)||'-'||split_part(begin_date,'-',1))::date AS begin_date,
		answered_at,
		recommendation 
	FROM {{ref('stg_whatsapp_nps_visits_cancelled')}} acv 
)
,scheduler_schedules AS (
	SELECT 
        schedule_id AS id, 
        begin_date
	FROM {{ref('proc_tmp_demand_schedules_cleaned')}}
	WHERE 
		STATUS = 'Cancelled'	
		AND begin_date BETWEEN '2022-01-08' AND '{{ var("processed_time") }}'::date
)
,clean_nps AS (
	SELECT 
        lower(nvc.country) AS country,
		nvc.visit_type,
		nvc.schedule_id,
		nvc.property_id,
		coalesce(nvc.begin_date,scheduler_schedules.begin_date) as begin_date,
		coalesce(answered_at,scheduler_schedules.begin_date,nvc.begin_date) AS formated_answer_timestamp,
		nvc.address,
		nvc.appraiser,
		nvc.recommendation::integer,
		nvc.comments
	FROM nps_visits_cancelled nvc 
	LEFT JOIN scheduler_schedules ON scheduler_schedules.id = nvc.schedule_id 
)
SELECT 
    clean_nps.*, 
	formated_answer_timestamp::date AS formated_answer_date,
	to_char(formated_answer_timestamp,'HH24:MI:SS') AS formated_answer_time 
FROM clean_nps

model.houm.proc_demand_schedules.raw_sql:
Select
    schedules.id        schedule_id 
    , prop_mz.geo_id
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.created_at)::timestamp with time zone)::date created_at
    , (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, schedules.begin_date)::timestamp with time zone)::date begin_date
    , schedules.prop_id property_id 
    , properties.supply_source
    , properties.supply_relation
    , schedules.status
    , scheduler_scheduletypes.name as schedule_type_name
    , applicant.email
    , applicant.id as  applicant_id 
from {{ ref('stg_scheduler_schedules') }} AS schedules
    left join {{ ref('stg_scheduler_scheduletypes') }} AS scheduler_scheduletypes on scheduler_scheduletypes.id  = schedules.schedule_type_id

model.houm.proc_demand_pipedrive_deals.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH proc_properties_mz AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }}  
)

, pipedrive_city AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('dim_pipedrive_city') }} 
)

, deals AS (
SELECT 
    id ,
    add_time ,
    email ,
    phone ,
    person_id , 
    CASE
        WHEN bi_deals.country_formated LIKE '%_hile%' THEN 79::INT
        WHEN bi_deals.country_formated LIKE '%_olombia%' THEN 14::INT
        WHEN bi_deals.country_formated LIKE '%__xico%' THEN 19::INT
        ELSE Null END AS geo_id_country_funnel ,
    CASE bi_deals.funnel 
        WHEN '1. Supply' THEN 'Supply' 
        WHEN '2. Demand' THEN 'Demand' 
        END AS funnel ,
    CASE 
        WHEN bi_deals.business IN ('2. Sales', '5. Sales Subsidio','5.1 Sales B2B' )    THEN 'Sales'
        WHEN bi_deals.business IN ('1. Rentals','3. Rental Alianzas' )                  THEN 'Rental'
        WHEN bi_deals.business IN ('4.1 Rental/Sales Alianzas', '4. Rental/Sales' )     THEN 'Rental & Sales'
        ELSE NULL END business ,
    CASE WHEN bi_deals.source like '%Autoperfilamiento%' THEN TRUE 
        ELSE FALSE END is_selfprofiling , 
    --- before negotiation
    --------------------
    bi_deals.marketing_id AS campaign_id , 
    bi_deals.source , 
    cities_source.geo_id as geo_id_source , 
    -- Demand 
    CASE 
        WHEN bi_deals.label = 345 THEN 'New Properties'
        WHEN bi_deals.label = 345 THEN 'Usados'
        ELSE NULL END AS buyer_relation_source   ,
    --- after negotiation
    --------------------
    COALESCE(proc_properties_mz.geo_id, cities_negotiation.geo_id) AS geo_id_negotiation , 
    bi_deals.property_id ,
    bi_deals.lead_buyer_type AS buyer_relation_negotiation ,
    -- Supply data 
    bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::date   AS supply_qualification_date , 
    bi_deals.qualification              AS supply_qualification ,
    -- Demand Data 
    CASE 
        WHEN bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::DATE < '2022-06-06'::DATE AND calificacion_buyer in (3,4,5) THEN coalesce(bi_deals.buyer_lead_qualification_date::DATE,bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::DATE)  
        WHEN bi_deals.fecha_calificacion::DATE < '2022-06-06'::DATE THEN NULL 
        ELSE bi_deals.buyer_lead_qualification_date::DATE 
        END AS buyer_qualification_date , 
    bi_deals.calificacion_buyer AS buyer_qualification , 
    -------------------
    bi_deals.lost_reason ,
    bi_deals.lost_time 
FROM {{ ref('stg_bi_deals') }} AS bi_deals
LEFT JOIN pipedrive_city AS cities_source 
    ON cities_source.city = bi_deals.city_3
LEFT JOIN pipedrive_city AS cities_negotiation
    ON cities_negotiation.city = bi_deals.city_2
LEFT JOIN proc_properties_mz
    ON proc_properties_mz.property_id = bi_deals.property_id
)

Select *
FROM deals

model.houm.proc_tmp_demand_schedules.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

SELECT
    a.id AS schedule_id,
    a.prop_id AS property_id,
    a.created_at,
    a.begin_date,
    timezone(e.timezone,timezone('UTC',a.created_at)) AS local_created_at,
    timezone(e.timezone,timezone('UTC',a.begin_date)) AS local_begin_date,
    b.name as schedule_type_name,
    CASE 
        WHEN lower(b.name) LIKE 'salesv%' THEN 'Visit'
        WHEN lower(b.name) LIKE 'salesp%' THEN 'Photo'
        ELSE b.name
    END AS schedule_name,
    a.status,
    CASE 
        WHEN lower(b.name) 
        LIKE '%sales%' THEN 'Sales'
        ELSE 'Rentals' 
    END AS business,
    a.cancel_reason,
    c.applicant_id,
    d.email,
    e.country,
    e.City_Houm AS city,
    e.supply_source,
    e.supply_relation,
    a.appraiser_id
FROM {{ref('stg_scheduler_schedules')}} a
LEFT JOIN {{ref('stg_scheduler_scheduletypes')}} b ON b.id = a.schedule_type_id
LEFT JOIN {{ref('stg_scheduler_schedulehasapplicant')}} c ON c.schedule_id = a.id
LEFT JOIN {{ref('stg_arriendoasegurado_applicant')}} d ON c.applicant_id = d.id
LEFT JOIN {{ref('proc_tmp_supply_properties_macrozone')}} e ON e.property_id = a.prop_id

WITH payments_cl AS (

    (timezone( prop_mz.timezone, movements.date::DATE)::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)::DATE AS thedate ,

    AND concept='RESERVATION'

    ON prop_mz.property_id = movements.property_id

    AND concept='RESERVATION' 
    AND type = 'INCOME'

)

    AND concept='RESERVATION' 
    AND type = 'INCOME'

)

)

model.houm.proc_demand_pipedrive_leads.raw_sql:
{{ config(materialized='table') }}

WITH properties AS (
SELECT 
    id , 
    supply_source ,
    supply_relation ,
    country 
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties') }}
)

, proc_properties_mz AS (
SELECT *
FROM {{ ref('proc_properties_mz') }}  
)

, demand_pipedrive_leads AS (
SELECT     
    -- Person details 
    persons.id AS person_id ,
    persons.name AS person_name ,
    COALESCE(persons.email , deals.email) AS email ,
    COALESCE(persons.phone , deals.phone) AS phone ,
    --- Pipedrive Info
    deals.id AS deal_id ,
    deals.add_time::DATE AS add_time  , 
    deals.funnel ,
    deals.business ,
    deals.geo_id_country_funnel ,
    deals.is_selfprofiling , 
    --- before negotiation
    deals.campaign_id , 
    deals.source , 
    geo_id_source , 
    -- Demand
    deals.buyer_relation_source ,
    --- after negotiation
    ---------------------------
    deals.property_id ,
    COALESCE( prop_mz.geo_id,  geo_id_negotiation, geo_id_country_funnel) AS geo_id_negotiation ,
    -- Supply data 
    --------------------
    deals.supply_qualification_date , 
    deals.supply_qualification , 
    -- Demand data
    --------------------
    CASE 
        WHEN  funnel = 'Demand' AND business LIKE '%Sales%' 
            THEN COALESCE( 
                        CASE 
                            WHEN properties.supply_source like 'New Properties' THEN properties.supply_source
                            WHEN properties.supply_source is not null THEN 'Usados'
                            END 
                        ,   buyer_relation_negotiation)
        ELSE NULL END  buyer_relation_negotiation ,
    properties.supply_relation ,
    properties.supply_source , 
    deals.buyer_qualification_date ,
    deals.buyer_qualification , 
    deals.lost_reason ,
    deals.lost_time 
FROM {{ref('proc_demand_pipedrive_deals')}} AS deals
LEFT JOIN {{ref('stg_bi_persons')}} AS persons
    ON deals.person_id = persons.id
LEFT JOIN proc_properties_mz AS prop_mz
    ON prop_mz.property_id = deals.property_id
LEFT JOIN properties 
    ON prop_mz.property_id = properties.id
WHERE add_time > '2022-01-01'::date
)

SELECT * 
FROM demand_pipedrive_leads
